-- ============================================================
-- NORMALIZATION SUMMARY
-- ============================================================

-- 1NF: No repeating groups ✓
--   - All columns atomic (no CSV, no JSON in data columns)
--   - Permissions in separate table (not CSV in roles)

-- 2NF: No partial key dependencies ✓
--   - Single-column PKs (user_id, role_id, permission_id)
--   - Composite keys (role_permissions) have all non-keys dependent on entire key

-- 3NF: No transitive dependencies ✓
--   - No non-key column depends on another non-key
--   - (e.g., role.role_name doesn't appear in users table)

-- BCNF: Every determinant is candidate key ✓
--   - All dependencies on actual keys
--   - No anomalies possible

